<h3>Upgrade to Flickr Companion</h3>

<p>Thank you for using FlickrFree! There is now a premium version of this app available on the Market.</p>

<p>It is called FlickrCompanion, and you can buy it for $.99. FlickrCompanion is based on the same code as 
FlickrFree, and offers all of the same features. In addition, it has the following features:</p>

<ul>
<li>Improved home screen UI.</li>
<li>Zoomable image views.</li>
</ul>

<p>Many improvements are in the pipeline for FlickrCompanion, including:</p>

<ul>
<li>A more thorough upload/download manager, allowing you to automatically sync your Flickr account with your phone's Media Gallery.</li>
<li>Better social features, such as notifications on your contacts' uploads.</li>
<li>Further interface improvements.</li>
</ul>

<p>If you wish to go to the market to purchase FlickrCompanion for $.99, please select "Upgrade". Otherwise, select "No Thanks", and you 
will not be asked again. However, you can always choose to upgrade by selecting the "Upgrade" link in the main window.</p>

